title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Cash 5' game
maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Cash 5” game were:
01-04-13-20-41
(one, four, thirteen, twenty, forty-one)
Estimated jackpot: $225,000
